OL,5,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FA team treats a man found injured
OL,7,     Fin the street. Initially it
OL,8,     Fappears he has been assualted, but
OL,9,     Ffurther investiagtion suggests he
OL,10,     Fmight be a drug user who tried to
OL,11,     Fbreak into a car.
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FAt the Hall Green Health Centre,
OL,14,     FDr Ashraf speaks to a man who has
OL,15,     Freturned from a holiday in Egypt
OL,16,     Fand may have picked up something
OL,17,     Fwith serious repercussions.
